#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:4
msgid "MicroPython manifest files"
msgstr "MicroPython清单文件"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:7
msgid "Summary"
msgstr "总结"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:9
msgid ""
"MicroPython has a feature that allows Python code to be \"frozen\" into "
"the firmware, as an alternative to loading code from the filesystem."
msgstr "MicroPython有一个功能，可以将Python代码\"冻结\"到固件中，作为从文件系统加载代码的替代方案。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:12
msgid "This has the following benefits:"
msgstr "这有以下好处:"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:14
msgid ""
"the code is pre-compiled to bytecode, avoiding the need for the Python "
"source to be compiled at load-time."
msgstr "代码被预编译为字节码，避免了在加载时编译Python源代码的需要。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:16
msgid ""
"the bytecode can be executed directly from ROM (i.e. flash memory) rather"
" than being copied into RAM. Similarly any constant objects (strings, "
"tuples, etc) are loaded from ROM also. This can lead to significantly "
"more memory being available for your application."
msgstr "字节码可以直接从ROM（即闪存）执行，而不是复制到RAM。类似地，任何常量对象（字符串、元组等）也可以从ROM加载。这可能会为您的应用程序提供更多的可用内存。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:20
msgid ""
"on devices that do not have a filesystem, this is the only way to load "
"Python code."
msgstr "在没有文件系统的设备上，这是加载Python代码的唯一方法。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:23
msgid ""
"During development, freezing is generally not recommended as it will "
"significantly slow down your development cycle, as each update will "
"require re-flashing the entire firmware. However, it can still be useful "
"to selectively freeze some rarely-changing dependencies (such as third-"
"party libraries)."
msgstr "在开发过程中，通常不建议冻结，因为它会显著降低开发周期，因为每次更新都需要重新刷新整个固件。但是，有选择地冻结一些很少更改的依赖项(例如第三方库)仍然是有用的。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:29
msgid ""
"The way to list the Python files to be frozen into the firmware is via a "
"\"manifest\", which is a Python file that will be interpreted by the "
"build process. Typically you would write a manifest file as part of a "
"board definition, but you can also write a stand-alone manifest file and "
"use it with an existing board definition."
msgstr "列出要冻结到固件中的 Python 文件的方法是通过\"manifest\"（清单），这是一个将由构建过程解释的 Python 文件。通常，您会编写一个清单文件作为板定义的一部分，但您也可以编写一个独立的清单文件，并将其与现有的板定义一起使用。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:35
msgid ""
"Manifest files can define dependencies on libraries from :term"
":`micropython-lib` as well as Python files on the filesystem, and also on"
" other manifest files."
msgstr "清单文件可以定义对:term: :term:`micropython-lib` 库的依赖，以及文件系统上的Python文件，也可以定义对其他清单文件的依赖。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:39
msgid "Writing manifest files"
msgstr "编写清单文件"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:41
msgid ""
"A manifest file is a Python file containing a series of function calls. "
"See the available functions defined below."
msgstr "manifest文件是包含一系列函数调用的Python文件。请参阅下面定义的可用函数。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:44
msgid ""
"Any paths used in manifest files can include the following variables. "
"These all resolve to absolute paths."
msgstr "清单文件中使用的任何路径都可以包含以下变量。这些都解析为绝对路径。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:47
msgid "``$(MPY_DIR)`` -- path to the micropython repo."
msgstr "``$(MPY_DIR)`` -- 指向micropython的路径。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:48
msgid ""
"``$(MPY_LIB_DIR)`` -- path to the micropython-lib submodule. Prefer to "
"use ``require()``."
msgstr "``$(MPY_LIB_DIR)`` -- micropython-lib子模块的路径。建议使用 ``require()``。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:50
msgid "``$(PORT_DIR)`` -- path to the current port (e.g. ``ports/stm32``)"
msgstr "``$(PORT_DIR)`` -- 当前移植版本的路径（例如：``ports/stm32``）"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:51
msgid ""
"``$(BOARD_DIR)`` -- path to the current board (e.g. "
"``ports/stm32/boards/PYBV11``)"
msgstr "``$(BOARD_DIR)`` -- 当前板的路径（例如：``ports/stm32/boards/PYBV11``）"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:54
msgid ""
"Custom manifest files should not live in the main MicroPython repository."
" You should keep them in version control with the rest of your project."
msgstr "自定义清单文件不应该存在于主MicroPython存储库中。您应该将它们与项目的其余部分一起放在版本控制中。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:57
msgid ""
"Typically a manifest used for compiling firmware will need to include the"
" port manifest, which might include frozen modules that are required for "
"the board to function. If you just want to add additional modules to an "
"existing board, then include the board manifest (which will in turn "
"include the port manifest)."
msgstr "通常用于编译固件的清单将需要包括移植清单，其中可能包括板运行所需的冻结模块。如果您只是想向现有的板添加额外的模块，那么包括板清单(这将依次包括移植清单)。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:63
msgid "Building with a custom manifest"
msgstr "使用自定义清单构建"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:65
msgid "Your manifest can be specified on the ``make`` command line with:"
msgstr "你的manifest可以在 ``make`` 命令行中指定:"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:71
msgid ""
"This applies to all ports, including CMake-based ones (e.g. esp32, rp2), "
"as the Makefile wrapper that will pass this into the CMake build."
msgstr "这适用于所有移植版本，包括基于CMake的移植版本(例如esp32, rp2)，因为Makefile包装器会将其传递到CMake构建中。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:75
msgid "Adding a manifest to a board definition"
msgstr "向板定义添加清单"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:77
msgid ""
"If you have a custom board definition, you can make it include your "
"custom manifest automatically. On make-based ports (most ports), in your "
"``mpconfigboard.mk`` set the ``FROZEN_MANIFEST`` variable."
msgstr ""
"如果您有一个自定义板定义，您可以使它自动包含您的自定义清单。在基于make的移植版本(大多数移植版本)上，在您的 "
"``mpconfigboard.mk`` 中设置 ``FROZEN_MANIFEST`` 变量。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:85
msgid ""
"On CMake-based ports (e.g. esp32, rp2), instead use "
"``mpconfigboard.cmake``"
msgstr "在基于CMake的移植版本(例如esp32, rp2)上，请使用 ``mpconfigboard.cmake``"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:92
msgid "High-level functions"
msgstr "高级功能"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:94
msgid ""
"Note: The ``opt`` keyword argument can be set on the various functions, "
"this controls the optimisation level used by the cross-compiler. See "
":func:`micropython.opt_level`."
msgstr ""
"注意:``opt`` "
"关键字参数可以在各种函数上设置，这控制了交叉编译器使用的优化级别。请参见:func:`micropython.opt_level`。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:100
msgid "Register the path to an external named *library*."
msgstr "注册外部命名 *library* 的路径。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:102
msgid ""
"The path *library_path* will be automatically searched when using "
"`require`. By default the added library is added to the end of the list "
"of libraries to search.  Pass ``True`` to *prepend* to add it to the "
"start of the list."
msgstr ""
"路径 *library_path* 在使用 `require` 时会自动被搜索。默认情况下，添加的库会被添加到库搜索列表的末尾。如果将 "
"``True`` 传递给 *prepend*，则会将其添加到列表的开头。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:106
msgid ""
"Additionally, the added library can be explicitly requested by using "
"``require(\"name\", library=\"library\")``."
msgstr "此外，可以通过使用 ``require(\"name\", library=\"library\")`` 显式请求添加的库。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:111
msgid ""
"This is equivalent to copying the \"package_path\" directory to the "
"device (except as frozen code)."
msgstr "这相当于将 \"package_path\" 目录复制到设备(冻结代码除外)。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:114
msgid ""
"In the simplest case, to freeze a package \"foo\" in the current "
"directory:"
msgstr "在最简单的情况下，冻结当前目录中的包 \"foo\":"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:120
msgid ""
"will recursively include all .py files in foo, and will be frozen as "
"``foo/**/*.py``."
msgstr "将递归包含foo中的所有 .py 文件，并将冻结为 ``foo/**/*.py``。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:123
msgid ""
"If the package isn't in the same directory as the manifest file, use "
"``base_path``:"
msgstr "如果包不在与manifest文件相同的目录中，请使用 ``base_path``:"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:129 ../../reference/manifest.rst:150
msgid "You can use the variables above, such as ``$(PORT_DIR)`` in ``base_path``."
msgstr "您可以使用上面的变量，例如 ``base_path`` 中的 ``$(PORT_DIR)`` 。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:131
msgid ""
"To restrict to certain files in the package use ``files`` (note: paths "
"should be relative to the package): ``package(\"foo\", "
"files=[\"bar/baz.py\"])``."
msgstr ""
"要限制包中的某些文件，请使用 ``files`` (注意:路径应该是相对于包的): ``package(\"foo\", "
"files=[\"bar/baz.py\"])`` 。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:136
msgid "Include a single Python file as a module."
msgstr "包括一个Python文件作为模块。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:138
msgid "If the file is in the current directory:"
msgstr "如果文件在当前目录中："

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:144
msgid "Otherwise use base_path to locate the file:"
msgstr "否则，请使用base_path定位文件："

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:154
msgid ""
"Require a package by name (and its dependencies) from :term:`micropython-"
"lib`."
msgstr "从 :term:`micropython-lib` 中按名称(及其依赖项)要求一个包。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:156
msgid ""
"Optionally specify *library* (a string) to reference a package from a "
"library that has been previously registered with `add_library`. Otherwise"
" the list of library paths will be used."
msgstr "可选地指定 *library* （一个字符串）来引用通过 `add_library` 之前注册的库中的包。否则，将使用库路径列表。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:162
msgid "Include another manifest."
msgstr "包括另一个清单。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:164
msgid ""
"Typically a manifest used for compiling firmware will need to include the"
" port manifest, which might include frozen modules that are required for "
"the board to function."
msgstr "通常用于编译固件的清单将需要包括移植清单，其中可能包括板运行所需的冻结模块。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:168
msgid ""
"The *manifest* argument can be a string (filename) or an iterable of "
"strings."
msgstr "*manifest* 参数可以是字符串(filename)或字符串可迭代对象。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:171
msgid "Relative paths are resolved with respect to the current manifest file."
msgstr "相对路径是根据当前清单文件解析的。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:173
msgid ""
"If the path is to a directory, then it implicitly includes the "
"manifest.py file inside that directory."
msgstr "如果路径指向一个目录，那么它隐式地包含该目录中的manifest.py文件。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:176
msgid ""
"You can use the variables above, such as ``$(PORT_DIR)`` in "
"``manifest_path``."
msgstr "您可以使用上面的变量，例如 ``manifest_path`` 中的 ``$(PORT_DIR)``。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:180
msgid ""
"Define metadata for this manifest file. This is useful for manifests for "
"micropython-lib packages."
msgstr "定义此清单文件的元数据。这对于micropython-lib包的清单很有用。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:184
msgid "Low-level functions"
msgstr "低级功能"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:186
msgid ""
"These functions are documented for completeness, but with the exception "
"of ``freeze_as_str`` all functionality can be accessed via the high-level"
" functions."
msgstr "为了完整起见，对这些函数进行了文档记录，但除了 ``freeze_as_str`` 之外，所有功能都可以通过高级函数访问。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:191
msgid ""
"Freeze the input specified by *path*, automatically determining its type."
"  A ``.py`` script will be compiled to a ``.mpy`` first then frozen, and "
"a ``.mpy`` file will be frozen directly."
msgstr ""
"冻结由 *path* 指定的输入，自动确定其类型。``.py`` 脚本将首先被编译为 ``.mpy`` 后冻结，然后一个 ``.mpy`` "
"文件将被直接冻结。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:195
msgid ""
"*path* must be a directory, which is the base directory to begin "
"searching for files.  When importing the resulting frozen modules, the "
"name of the module will start after *path*, i.e. *path* is excluded from "
"the module name."
msgstr "*path* 必须是一个目录，它是开始搜索文件的基目录。当导入结果冻结的模块时，模块的名称将以 *path* 开头，即 *path* 从模块名称中排除。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:200
msgid "If *path* is relative, it is resolved to the current ``manifest.py``."
msgstr "如果 *path* 是相对的，它被解析为当前的 ``manifest.py``。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:202
msgid "If *script* is None, all files in *path* will be frozen."
msgstr "如果 *script* 为None，*path* 中的所有文件将被冻结。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:204
msgid ""
"If *script* is an iterable then ``freeze()`` is called on all items of "
"the iterable (with the same *path* and *opt* passed through)."
msgstr "如果 *script* 是一个可迭代对象，那么对可迭代对象的所有项调用 ``freeze()`` (传递相同的 *path* 和 *opt*)。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:207
msgid ""
"If *script* is a string then it specifies the file or directory to "
"freeze, and can include extra directories before the file or last "
"directory.  The file or directory will be searched for in *path*.  If "
"*script* is a directory then all files in that directory will be frozen."
msgstr "如果 *script* 是一个字符串，那么它指定要冻结的文件或目录，并且可以在文件或最后一个目录之前包含额外的目录。文件或目录将在 *path* 中搜索。如果 *script* 是一个目录，那么该目录下的所有文件将被冻结。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:212
msgid ""
"*opt* is the optimisation level to pass to mpy-cross when compiling "
"``.py`` to ``.mpy``.  These levels are described in "
":func:`micropython.opt_level`."
msgstr ""
"*opt* 是在编译 ``.py`` 到 ``.mpy`` 时传递给mpy-cross的优化级别。这些级别在 "
":func:`micropython.opt_level` 中描述。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:217
msgid ""
"Freeze the given *path* and all ``.py`` scripts within it as a string, "
"which will be compiled upon import."
msgstr "冻结给定的 *path* 和其中的所有 ``.py`` 脚本作为字符串，该字符串将在导入时编译。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:222
msgid ""
"Freeze the input by first compiling the ``.py`` scripts to ``.mpy`` "
"files, then freezing the resulting ``.mpy`` files.  See ``freeze()`` for "
"further details on the arguments."
msgstr ""
"先将 ``.py`` 脚本编译为 ``.mpy`` 文件，然后冻结生成的 ``.mpy`` 文件。有关参数的更多详细信息，请参阅 "
"``freeze()`` 。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:228
msgid ""
"Freeze the input, which must be ``.mpy`` files that are frozen directly. "
"See ``freeze()`` for further details on the arguments."
msgstr "冻结输入，必须是直接冻结的 ``.mpy`` 文件。有关参数的更多详细信息，请参阅 ``freeze()``。"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:232
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

