msgid ""
"To freeze a directory of files in a subdirectory \"mydriver\" of the "
"current directory which will be available as ``import mydriver``, use:"
msgstr "要冻结当前目录的子目录\"mydriver\"中的文件目录，该目录将以 ``import mydriver`` 的形式可用，使用:"

