msgid "Then the board can be compiled with"
msgstr "然后用板进行编译"

#: ../../reference/manifest.rst:273
msgid ""
"Note that most boards do not have their own ``manifest.py``, rather they "
"use the port one directly, in which case your manifest should just "
"``include(\"$(PORT_DIR)/boards/manifest.py\")`` instead."
msgstr ""
"请注意，大多数板没有自己的 ``manifest.py``，而是直接使用一个移植版本，在这种情况下，你的清单应该只需 "
"``include(\"$(PORT_DIR)/boards/manifest.py\")`` 。"

